<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: #0f172a;
            color: #e2e8f0;
        }

        header {
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #e2e8f0;
            margin-left: 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .hero {
            height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .hero p {
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #3b82f6;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .section {
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .projects {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: #1e293b;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>MyPortfolio</h1>
    <nav>
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">About</a>
        <a href="#">Projects</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <h2>Salom, men Web Developer</h2>
    <p>Minimalistik va zamonaviy saytlar yarataman</p>
    <button class="btn">Bog‘lanish</button>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Men haqimda</h2>
    <p>Men frontend va backend bilan ishlovchi dasturchiman. Zamonaviy texnologiyalarni o‘rganaman.</p>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Loyihalarim</h2>
    <div class="projects">
        <div class="card">Project 1</div>
        <div class="card">Project 2</div>
        <div class="card">Project 3</div>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    © 2026 MyPortfolio
</footer>

</body>
</html>
